{"word":"προσπλέω","slug":"προσπλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσπλέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πλεύσομαι</el>) (ionic <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> <el>-πλώω</el>) (<a href='S:aorist tense'>aor.</a>1 <el>προσέπλωσα</el>) </el><p/><i>to sail towards</i> or <i>against</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τινί</el> <i>against</i> one, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; of ships, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}